MASS panel: 
1. Design Aspect: 
- add label " Converting Mass"
- add combo-box 
 - change elements to "mg to g to g, mg to kg, g to mg, g to kg, kg to mg, kg to g" 
- add label " Enter value"
- add textfield
- add textfield
- add button "convert"

2. Coding  (similar code format for other conversion panels)
- int m = 1000; 
- int n = 1000000; 
- int mass1 = getText from textfieldValue 
when ConvertButton is clicked: 
if (item of ComboBox1 selected == "mg to g")
  { mg divide by 1000 
  int mg2g = mg/m                                   
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show mg2g on textfieldResult }
  
  else if (item of Combbox1 selected == "mg to kg" )
  { mg times by 1000000
  int mg2kg = mg*n; 
  format 2 decimnal places 
  show mg2kg on textfieldResult
  }
  
  else if (item of Combbox1 selected == "g to mg" )
  { g divide by 1000
  int g2mg = g/m; 
  format 2 decimnal places 
  show  g2mg on textfieldResult
  }


  else if (item of Combbox1 selected == "g to kg" )
  { g times by 1000
  int g2kg = mg*m; 
  format 2 decimnal places 
  show g2kg on textfieldResult
  }

 
  else if (item of Combbox1 selected == "kg to mg" )
  { kg divide by 1000000
  int kg2mg = kg*n; 
  format 2 decimnal places 
  show kg2mg on textfieldResult
  }
  
   
  else (item of Combbox1 selected == "kg to g" )
  { kg divide by 1000
  int kg2g = kg*m; 
  format 2 decimnal places 
  show kg2g on textfieldResult
  }

time panel: 

if (item of ComboBox selected == "seconds to minutes")
  { time *60                             
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }

        
else if (item of ComboBox selected == "seconds to hours")
  { time *3600                             
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }
  
  
  else if (item of ComboBox selected == "minutes to seconds")
    { time/60                             
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }

  else if (item of ComboBox selected == "minutes to hours")
    { time/60                            
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }

    else if (item of ComboBox selected == "hours to minutes")
    { time*60                            
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }
 
  else if (item of ComboBox selected == "hours to seconds")
    { time*3600                            
  format 2 decimnal places **decimals places may vary
  show time on textfieldResult }
  



